thread.title: Julia Vosnakis

author: Julia Vosnakis
title: Julia Vosnakis
text: Great selection of products and prices even after conversion to AUD! Only slightly worried about the VIP membership charging my account if I forget each month to skip suggested outfits, but just mean I need to set my self a reminder for myself. Hopefully I'll be able to cancel VIP membership easily form Australia if need be. Very excited to received my purchases and hoping if needed that refunds/ store credit goes well.
